    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏背景】</h2><br>哥伦布？麦哲伦？德雷克？还是郑和？无敌舰队最终陨落谁家？<br>《航海纷争》是基于中世纪资源掠夺航海为主题的策略战争养成类游戏！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/ebf2fc6d03339eaf5a9a6a40f56da5bc.poster.avif?t=1691718712\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/ebf2fc6d03339eaf5a9a6a40f56da5bc.webm?t=1691718712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/ebf2fc6d03339eaf5a9a6a40f56da5bc.mp4?t=1691718712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>玩家作为一名睿智和霸气的航海冒险家，打造属于自己的海上航海舰队，用您的智谋和策略去打败对手的超级航海舰队。<br><br>世界？版图？去称霸大航海时代！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏特色】</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 真实港口，丰富关卡</h2>真实宏大的海港地图，完美的画面，还原了当时各地的港口与地名，呈现出不同的特色。丰富的关卡探索大幅提升了冒险的拟真度与趣味性，游戏涵盖了探险、海战等丰富玩法，为航海家们构造出无比庞大的真实航海世界。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/634cd58e85fb3b23058c8c3de7974b81.poster.avif?t=1691718712\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/634cd58e85fb3b23058c8c3de7974b81.webm?t=1691718712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/634cd58e85fb3b23058c8c3de7974b81.mp4?t=1691718712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 酷炫画面、超爽战斗</h2>全民航海大战，激情攻打世界大BOSS，全服玩家一起合作！<br>使用多样的策略打败海盗，和联盟成员合作，消灭海怪，海量奖励等你来拿！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/3bf5cc7e8283e346365f3ae7c17e3183.poster.avif?t=1691718712\" width=615 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/3bf5cc7e8283e346365f3ae7c17e3183.webm?t=1691718712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 激情对战、策略为王</h2>前船开路后船护航，配合联盟火力全开；交叉防御密集打击，来犯舰队灰飞烟灭！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/27275c9e161ed17c697afa1a0dafd388.poster.avif?t=1691718712\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/27275c9e161ed17c697afa1a0dafd388.webm?t=1691718712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377910/extras/27275c9e161ed17c697afa1a0dafd388.mp4?t=1691718712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 无敌舰队，王者归来</h2>积攒材料，强化自己的舰船的各个部件，在对战中获取更多的资源，打造属于自己的舰队；战乱时代实力为王，升级联盟称霸海权！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >向着星辰大海，正式启航</h2>",
